        =======
        History
        =======
        
        0.1.0 (2020-03-24)
        ------------------
        * Supported formats (csv, burmeister, fimi, matlab (version<=7))
        * Basic CLI implemented
        
        0.1.1 (2020-04-7)
        -----------------
        * Added Conexp format support
        * Added support of Python 3.5, 3.6
        
        0.1.2 (2020-04-17)
        ------------------
        * Rewritten to bitarray under the hood (less memory needed)
        
